  <brief_title>A Clinical Study in Children and Adolescents With Mild to Moderate Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Double-blind Clinical Study to Examine the Efficacy and Safety of Zarzenda in Comparison to Elidel in the Management of Mild to Moderate Atopic Dermatitis in Children and Adolescents</official_title>
  <sponsors>
